description:
PalmOS Timeline gives you the opportunity to remember all PalmOS based devices ever created.
************************************
Features : Browse PalmOS device list or just type, name, manufacturer, release date, processor , frequency, memory,… | For each PalmOS device, get related pictures, wikipedia article, youtube videos, full specs, reviews… | Full Screen Mode | Cross Fading transtition between articles | Instant Swipe Back for a faster browsing experience | Save articles to bookmarks | Page Top & bottom shortcuts.
************************************
Share : Online Bookmarks & Read it later support : Relego, Spare time | Facebook and Facebook beta support | Twitter Clients support : Spaz, Twee, Bad kitty, Yak, Tweed, TweetMe | Customize Statuses +short URL maker | I.M or Email support | Copy URL to clipboard
